# Project Workflow

## General

- Ask clarifying questions when the prompt needs more information.
- You may edit any file in this repo without waiting for approval.
- Always write test cases when implementing something new or modifying existing behavior.
- Always update `README.md` in both `frontend` and `backend` when logic, features, or other documented behavior changes.

## Git

When any file is changed, modified, or added:

1. Run the relevant tests.
2. If all tests pass, automatically `git commit` and `git push`.
